sequenceDiagram
  participant User
  participant App as "Procurement App"
  participant DB as "MongoDB"
  participant HIS as "HIS (FHIR)"
  participant Email as "Mail Relay"
  User->>App: Submit procurement request
  App->>DB: Persist request
  App->>HIS: (optional) Resolve department identifier
  App-->>User: Ack receipt
  DeptHead->>App: Review & approve
  App->>Procurement: Notify procurement officer
  Procurement->>App: Create PO
  App->>Email: Send notifications
